## Proposed Changes

### Files to Create

**1. Print styles (embedded in existing CSS)**

Add to `src/index.css` or create `src/styles/print.css`:

```css
@media print {
  /* Hide dashboard navigation */
  header,
  nav,
  .sidebar,
  footer,
  button:not(.print-preserve),
  .no-print {
    display: none !important;
  }

  /* Optimize layout for paper */
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: white !important;
    color: black !important;
  }

  /* Calendar container */
  .calendar-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1cm;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  /* Calendar header (print) */
  .calendar-header {
    margin-bottom: 1cm;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
    padding-bottom: 0.5cm;
  }

  /* Week/Month grid */
  .calendar-grid {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }

  .calendar-grid th,
  .calendar-grid td {
    border: 1px solid #333;
    padding: 0.3cm;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: black !important;
    background: white !important;
  }

  /* Events in print */
  .calendar-event {
    background: #f0f0f0 !important;
    border: 1px solid #666 !important;
    color: black !important;
    padding: 2mm;
    margin: 1mm 0;
    font-size: 9pt;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }

  /* Landscape orientation hint */
  @page {
    size: landscape;
    margin: 1cm;
  }

  /* Dark mode overrides */
  * {
    color-adjust: exact;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }
}
```

