## Design Considerations

### Design System Compliance
- **Colors:** Print always uses black text on white (ignore dark mode)
- **Components:** Print button uses same style as view switcher buttons
- **Typography:** Print uses 10pt for calendar grid, 9pt for events
- **Spacing:** 1cm margins, 0.3cm padding in cells
- **No gradients:** Print is black/white only (cost-effective, readable)

### Performance
- **Bundle Size Impact:** +0 KB (CSS doesn't affect JS bundle)
- **Print styles:** ~50 lines CSS in `@media print` block
- **Lazy Loading:** Not needed (CSS loaded with page)

### Accessibility
- **Keyboard Nav:** Print button accessible via Tab key
- **Screen Reader:** `title="Print calendar"` attribute
- **Focus States:** Same as other header buttons
- **Print-friendly:** Black/white output, sufficient contrast

### Print Optimization
- **Page size:** A4 / Letter (standard)
- **Orientation:** Landscape (fits more columns)
- **Margins:** 1cm all around
- **Font sizes:** 10pt grid headers, 9pt events (readable when printed)
- **Colors:** Black/white only (no colored backgrounds)
- **Page breaks:** Avoid breaking events across pages

