## Implementation Notes

### Decisions Made
- **2025-11-18** - Use embedded `@media print` in index.css instead of separate print.css (simpler)
- **2025-11-18** - Landscape orientation by default (fits week/month views better)
- **2025-11-18** - Black/white only print (no color backgrounds - saves ink, more professional)
- **2025-11-18** - Hide ALL buttons except preserve print button briefly (then hide in print CSS)

### Challenges Anticipated
- **Challenge:** Dark mode styles leak into print
  - **Solution:** `color-adjust: exact` + force black/white in print CSS
  - **Test:** Print from dark mode, verify no dark backgrounds

- **Challenge:** Calendar grid might not fit on one page
  - **Solution:** Use landscape + small font sizes (10pt/9pt)
  - **Alternative:** Add `@page { size: A3 landscape; }` for larger calendars

- **Challenge:** Events with long titles overflow cells
  - **Solution:** `page-break-inside: avoid` + `word-wrap: break-word`
  - **Test:** Print calendar with long event titles

### Deviations from Plan
- None anticipated - straightforward CSS + button implementation

